source.name: National Center for Education Statistics (NCES) -  Integrated Postsecondary Education Data System (IPEDS) - Institutional Characteristics - Directory Information - 2011 - API
source.description: The directory information for every institution in the 2011 IPEDS universe.  Includes name, address, city, state, zipcode and various URL links to the institution's home page, admissions, financial aid offices and  the net price calculator.  Identifies institutions as currently active, institutions that participate in Title IV federal financial aid programs for which IPEDS is mandatory.  It also includes variables derived from the 2011 Institutional Characteristics survey, such as control and level of institution, highest level and highest degree offered and carnegie classifications.
